Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
Hello. I would like to see an apartment please.

Scenario.UserTask: You are interested in viewing an apartment. Please schedule a viewing at Shadyside Apartments for Friday at 7 pm. Your name is John. You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee.
